{"tid":983578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【弒母判囚30年】肢解阿媽分成七袋藏雪櫃 華裔男：對不起，媽媽","createTime":"2019-01-16T05:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T21:20:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"08b76bc001e8f41cfb88c4ee6ea004240813912a","tid":983578,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"美國夏威夷檀香山華裔男子龔宇偉（Yu Wei Gong，音譯）涉嫌於2016年9月殺害並肢解母親。審訊於周一結束，龔宇偉被判誤殺罪成，加上盜用他人身份及非法處理屍體罪，共判監30年。龔表示，自己不值得家人原諒，並希望對母親說「對不起」。<br />\n現年28歲的龔宇偉涉嫌於2016年9月殺害母親龔柳雲（Liu Yun Gong，音譯），肢解屍體藏於雪櫃超過半年，他在2017年4月企圖自殺後報警自首，被控二級謀殺。他承認誤殺罪，以換取免除終身監禁。<br />\n周一判刑時，龔在庭上大部份時間低頭，又向居於中國和夏威夷的家人道歉，表示︰「我為我做過的事而感到羞愧。對不起，媽媽。」他又認為自己不值得家人原諒，其辯護律師稱︰「我希望澄清一點，他（龔）很愛他的母親，她是位好媽媽，這種事絕不應該發生在她身上。」<br />\n王姓法官（Paul Wong，音譯）判被告誤殺罪成入獄20年，另龔因在殺人後利用母親的賬戶交租，故被判盜用他人身份罪判囚10年，須分開服刑；一項非法處理屍體罪，判監一年可同時執行。假釋委員會將商議龔的最低刑期，檢控官建議最少監禁20年。<br />\n龔向警方表示，因為想放棄學業出外工作，激怒媽媽，去年9月意外殺死她。而驗屍報告指，她死因是頭部受鈍力所傷。警方在龔的寓所，在冰格檢獲七袋屍塊，包括2隻手臂和頭顱，由於屍體已被碎屍，最後要以指紋鑑定身份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547535828_1902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547535828_1902.jpg&h=b0deb997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190116/59144709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59144709&d=SX%2BUoBDMe9%2BAxfAiwDzPbIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=ed446533\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59144709&h=efbc6fb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190116/59144709</a>"},{"pid":"dee27cef61acd4ad790b353e9f72a10bb3699211","tid":983578,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"魂。初弒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c768484f96f8328597108e14b422abae2100a12c","tid":983578,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dee27cef61acd4ad790b353e9f72a10bb3699211","tid":983578,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"魂。初弒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cfdc0af88f140ec8e8e05c9e202f87e4ea18ea","tid":983578,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T21:04:07.000Z","msg":"叫你讀書要俾你分屍 香港嗰啲老母推尻你去做野搵錢俾家用又唔見被分屍"},{"pid":"ac09beb79e112c1921ede0c6d90001e4999df564","tid":983578,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T21:20:42.000Z","msg":"斬開18碌都可以係誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出黎都5，6張野<br />\nYu Wei的孤寂 多麼孤寂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}